FEDERAL NATIONAL MORTGAGE ASSOCIATION, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Stanley CLARK, Fay Clark, his wife, Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation as Receiver for Indy Mac Federal Bank, FSB, Defendants,
and
Burnett Manor Condominium Association, Defendant-Petitioner. C-855 September Term 2018
082490 Supreme Court of New Jersey. MAY 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004132-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
